        Application Plan (Updated):
        - Goal: Update the interactive portfolio planner for the Level 3 Content Creator Apprenticeship with the latest KSBs.
        - Structure: Retain the two-panel SPA layout.
        - Left Panel (Sidebar): Navigation buttons have been updated to reflect the new KSB categories: Regulatory, Written Content, Audio-visual, etc.
        - Right Panel (Main Content): KSB cards are now regrouped under the new section headings and populated with the new descriptions.
        - Interaction: The core JavaScript functionality remains. Clicking a "map tag" (e.g., K5) highlights all related KSBs. The mapping logic has been updated to reflect the relationships within the new KSB set.
        - Styling: Continues to use Tailwind CSS with the "Creative Spark" indigo theme.
        - Technology: Vanilla JavaScript for interactivity.
